Program: Outlook
Title: Caught in the Crossfire with Malala
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p02dcqfn
Last Broadcast Date: Thu 11 Dec 2014
In October 2012 Kainat Riaz and Shazia Ramzan were injured alongside Malala Yousafzai on the school bus when she was attacked by the Taliban. From a Durban township to the stage of London's Royal Opera House - the soaring career of South African baritone Njabulo Madlala. Christopher Jefferies is a retired school teacher who in 2010 was wrongly accused of a high-profile murder. Now a film has been made about his ordeal, directed by a former pupil of his, Roger Michell. Show less